Combine juice and SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener in small saucepan. Bring to a boil, reduce heat, and simmer, stirring occasionally, 20 to 25 minutes or until reduced to 1/3 cup. Cool at room temperature. Preheat broiler with rack about 4 inches from heat. Arrange grapefruit slices in single layer in large baking dish. Sprinkle with SPLENDA(R) Sugar Blend. Broil grapefruit slices 8 minutes or until fruit is flecked with brown. Arrange on serving platter or individual plates and drizzle with pomegranate syrup.